        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="6">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--cyan-bg);color:var(--cyan)"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">06</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Employee Onboarding</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Digital onboarding with document collection and checklist. Get new hires productive from day one.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="7">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--blue-bg);color:var(--blue)"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">07</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Shift Management</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Flexible shift scheduling with rotation and swap capabilities. Handle complex shift patterns effortlessly.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="8">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--purple-bg);color:var(--purple)"><i class="fa-solid fa-hand-holding-dollar"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">08</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Loan & Advance</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Employee loan management with automatic EMI deduction from salary. Track disbursement and recovery.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="9">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--orange-bg);color:var(--orange)"><i class="fa-solid fa-door-open"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">09</span>
