        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="11">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--pink-bg);color:var(--pink)"><i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">11</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Performance Appraisal</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Goal setting, KRA/KPI tracking, and appraisal cycles. Drive performance with structured evaluation.</p>
        </div>
